                    <span>More people should read this book. Anybody with any interest in language, communication, artificial intelligence or any area where ideas are conveyed abstractly will benefit from a reading of this book. This book provides powerful and rigourous tools for examining communication. No student of language/linguistics, logic, comp-sci, e.t.c. should leave this book unread.</span>
                  
              
